name: Pretty Boy
description:
Pretty Boy - generates handsome faces of male model beauty standards, without a beard.

This is my first attempt at making and share a AI model, so I'd love some feedback to improve next versions.


Trained on SD 1.5
Triggers with Pretty Boy. You can also control the appearance with the words: Caucasian Black Asian Indian


To improve results recommended:
VAE sd-vae-ft-mse-original

For more stylized versions, I used:
NED

I also tried it with LORA:
SamDoesArts
Hipoly 3D Model

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight according to the instructions (by default it's :1)
